name: File Not Found (Free Food Studios)
description:
FILE NOT FOUND

File Not Found is an exploration/walking simulator game, where you explore the disaster that is my Godot project list while gazing upon my attempt to actually finish a project for once by piecing something together from my older projects. This is basically a vent game. I am sorry.

Made for Godot Wild Jam #45, with the theme of Underground, where I took it in a less literal direction.

NOTE - It doesn't run the best on HTML5, I apologize for the stutter.

CONTROLS
  • Keyboard / Mouse
    • WASD / Arrow Keys - Movement
    • E / Space / Enter - Interact
    • Escape - Pause
  • Controller
    • Left Joystick / D-Pad - Movement
    • A Button (Bottom Face Button) - Interact
    • "Start/Options" Button - Pause
